- The "extra data" member of the gaim_conversation
  structure will be used to store encryption session
  information related to the particular conversation.
  Any such field is prefixed with `grypt_'.

  These fields include:

+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
| Type			| Field		| Description		|
+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
| GtkWidget *		| button	| GTK button widget	|
| int *			| state		| Session crypto state	|
| GpgmeRecipients *	| rep		| Gpgme recipient	|
+-----------------------+---------------+-----------------------+
